md: Maggie sets her sights on Danny-Lee's rival moonshine operation
. She asks you to find her old stash of explosives, head to Lag
ras, and take down the competition.

string: Search ~o~Scarlett Meadows~s~ for the ~o~stash of explosives~s~
Players dismount in front of Maggie asking how it went. The Posse Leader nods head. Maggie asks if Danny Lee was there.
A wagon with Danny-Lee Bart and Lemoyne Raider Guards arrive, dismount and approach the players/Maggie.
After discussion Danny-Lee and Bart go back to the wagon and leave.
Destroy Danny-Lee's moonshine business in Lagras.
